Return leaflet icon set for FIB maps

Source: R/util_fibicons.R
util_fibicons.Rd

Return leaflet icon set for FIB maps

Usage

util_fibicons(indic)

Arguments

indic

character indicating "entero", "entero&ecoli", or "fibmat" for Enterococcus, Fecal Enterococcus and E. coli, or FIB matrix maps, respectively

Value

A leaflet icon set as returned by iconList.

Details

Used internally with show_enteromap for wet/dry icons for Enterococcus, with show_fibmap for E. Coli/Enterococcus icons (EPCHC data), and with show_fibmatmap for matrix annual score category icons for EPCHC and non-EPCHC data.

Examples

util_fibicons(indic = 'entero')
#> $entero_green_wet
#> $iconUrl
#> [1] "/home/runner/work/_temp/Library/tbeptools/ecoli_green.png"
#> 
#> $iconWidth
#> [1] 18
#> 
#> $iconHeight
#> [1] 18
